title: Bug 116564: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.
OB: The title of hyperlink builder is changing with the settings.
EB: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', regardless of the settings.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'.
2. Click on 'OK' to confirm.
3. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
